urdu transliteration text:
Tere baba babul hawaij hainUska sikka jahaa me raij haiHam to har imtehaa se guzrengeDene wala wohi nataij hai
His coin is used world wide
@HujjatELC

Tera dada Imam Sadiq haiJiske dam se hai jafferi saareDeen o mazhab sabak ibadat haiHam ko saye usi ke darse mile
Through whose efforts we are all Ja’fferi today
@HujjatELC

Hai qaramate murtaza tujhmeSaailo ko bhi yet ata tujhmeRad jo hoti nahi kisi suratSaans keti hai woh dua tujhme
No requests are ever turned away
@HujjatELC
